infrastructure:
I-Geo iyithuluzi elinamandla lokuqapha ukwakhiwa nokugcinwa kokunakekelwa kwengqalasizinda nezinsiza, ikakhulukazi ezindaweni lapho ukuntuleka kwemisebenzi kwentsha kuphezulu futhi inkohlakalo ingaba yinkinga. Nge-Geo, bangakwazi ukulandelela inqubekelaphambili nekhwalithi ngesikhathi sangempela, baqinisekise ukuthi amaphrojekthi aqedwa ngesikhathi nangaphakathi kwesabelomali, futhi bakhombe futhi baxazulule izinkinga ezingaba khona ngaphambi kokuba zibe izinkinga ezinkulu.
Ngokusebenzisa amandla okuqapha i-Geo multimedia, i-ejensi ingaphinda ithuthukise ukubonakala kanye nokuziphendulela, okungasiza ukulwa nenkohlakalo nokwakha ukwethembana nomphakathi.
Ekugcineni, i-Geo ingasiza i-ejensi ukuthi ikhulise umthelela wokutshalwa kwayo kungqalasizinda nezinye izikhungo, kuyilapho iphinde idale amathuba entsheni engasebenzi ukuze ibambe iqhaza ekuqapheni nasekufakeni isandla ekuthuthukisweni kwemiphakathi yayo.
govt:
Izikhungo zikahulumeni nezikhulu zingazuza ku-Geo ngezindlela ezimbalwa. Okokuqala, i-Geo ingasiza ekulawuleni ngendlela efanele nangempumelelo amaphrojekthi wengqalasizinda ngokunikeza ukuqapha nokubika kwesikhathi sangempela se-multimedia, okungasiza ekuhlonzeni nasekuxazululeni noma yiziphi izinkinga ezingase ziphakame phakathi nephrojekthi. Okwesibili, i-Geo ingasiza ekulweni nenkohlakalo ngokukhiqiza irekhodi elinenhloso nelingaqinisekiswa lenqubekelaphambili yephrojekthi kanye nezindleko, ezingasiza ekuvimbeleni noma ekutholeni imisebenzi yokukhwabanisa.
Okwesithathu, i-Geo inganikeza imininingwane ebalulekile ngezidingo nezinto ezibalulekile emiphakathini, engasiza izikhungo zikahulumeni ukuthi ziqondise kangcono izinsiza nemizamo yazo lapho zidingeka khona kakhulu. Okokugcina, ngokuzibandakanya kanye nokunika abantu abasha amandla ohlelweni lokuqapha nokubika ngamaphrojekthi wengqalasizinda, i-Geo ingasiza ekwakheni umuzwa wobunikazi nokuzibophezela entsheni, kuyilapho futhi ibanika amakhono abalulekile nolwazi olungasiza ekuthuthukiseni amathuba abo okuqashwa. .
community:
Amaqembu omphakathi angazibandakanya ne-Geo ngokusebenzisa inkundla ukuze aqaphe futhi aphathe amaphrojekthi awo asekelwe emphakathini, njengemikhankaso yokuhlanza umphakathi, imizamo yokuvolontiya, noma imicimbi yokuqongelela imali. Inkundla ingaphinda isetshenziselwe ukulandelela inqubekelaphambili yala maphrojekthi kanye nokuqinisekisa ukuthi izinsiza zabiwa ngempumelelo. Ukwengeza, amaqembu omphakathi angasebenzisa i-Geo ukubika izehlakalo noma izinkinga emphakathini wawo, njengobugebengu noma izingozi zemvelo, futhi alandelele impendulo yeziphathimandla ezifanele.
Lokhu kungasiza ekwenzeni ngcono ukuphepha komphakathi futhi kukhuthaze ukubambisana okukhulu phakathi kwamalungu omphakathi nama-ejensi kahulumeni wendawo. Okokugcina, amaqembu omphakathi angasebenzisa i-Geo ukuze axhumanise imizamo yokuzithandela ngesikhathi sezimo eziphuthumayo, njengezinhlekelele zemvelo, futhi aqinisekise ukuthi izinsiza zinikezwa labo abadinga usizo.
youth:
Uma kubhekwa ukusabalala kwama-smartphones kanye nokusetshenziswa kwemidiya yedijithali entsheni, i-Geo ingaba ithuluzi elibalulekile lokubandakanya nokuqasha intsha kumaphrojekthi okuthuthukisa umphakathi. Izikhundla zabasebenzi basezindaweni kungenzeka ziqondiswe ngqo entsheni ekhululekile ngokusebenzisa ama-smartphones kanye nemidiya yedijithali, okungenzeka ukuthi ibikade ingasebenzi. Ngaphezu kwalokho, ukuzibandakanya ne-Geo kunganikeza intsha amakhono omsebenzi abalulekile nolwazi lomsebenzi, okungakhuphula ukuqashwa kwayo esikhathini esizayo.
Ukwengeza, ngokuzibandakanya nentsha nokubabandakanya ezinhlelweni zokuthuthukiswa komphakathi, i-Geo ingasiza ekukhuthazeni umuzwa wokuziqhenya kanye nobunikazi emiphakathini yayo, okungaholela ekwandeni kokuzibandakanya nokubamba iqhaza esikhathini esizayo.
